Package: TidyComb
Type: Package
Title: Preparing drug combination data for DrugComb 
Version: 0.0.16
Date: 2020-03-30
Author: person("Shuyu", "Zheng", email = "shuyu.zheng@helsinki.fi",
    role = c("aut", "cre")) 
     person("Jing", "Tang", email = "jing.tang@helsinki.fi",
    role = c("aut", "cre")) 
Maintainer: Shuyu Zheng <shuyu.zheng@helsinki.fi>
Description: This package wrapped the functions that could be used to tidy drug
    combination data from various sources into the format that is required by 
    uploading to DrugComb database. It includes functions for retrieving drug 
    information from chemistry databases: PubChem and Chembl, retrieving cell 
    line information from Cellosaurus, calculating drug synergy and sensitivity
    scores, etc.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
License: Mozilla Public License 2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: 
    XML, RCurl, jsonlite, dplyr, plyr, reshape2, drc, nleqslv, gplots,
    magrittr, stats, utils, foreach, doParallel, rlang, adabag,
    ape, synergyfinder (>= 2.0.1)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Suggests: 
    testthat, knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
